ibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">仅依赖理论上的数据。由于理论的数据，会排除掉其他各种干扰，而真实情况中，会增加很多限制逻辑。假如不实际测试，很容易就卡在某个被自己忽略的因素上。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">仅依赖于权威人士。因为权威人士没有深入到具体的业务中，很可能不清楚具体业务的限制。而你由于对技术没有深入的理解，也不会把影响技术性能的所有因素都汇总起来。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">自己必须针对核心应用场景，简化场景，然后测试可用性。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">本人在设计流式抓取技术方案的时候，就遇到这个问题。对数据从</font>mysql<font face="宋体">中读取的时候，根据最快的速度，速度应该是</font><font face="Calibri">30M/s</font><font face="宋体">，而真正实施的时候，发现</font><font face="Calibri">30M</font><font face="宋体">最快也需要</font><font face="Calibri">3s</font><font face="宋体">。虽然网卡速度很快，但是</font><font face="Calibri">python</font><font face="宋体">解析数据加载入内存却很慢。最坑的是在插入数据的时候，日常会在</font><font face="Calibri">10</font><font face="宋体">分钟执行完的程序，因为目标</font><font face="Calibri">mysql</font><font face="宋体">表有</font><font face="Calibri">unique key</font><font face="宋体">，导致批量插入数据处于</font><font face="Calibri">7</font><font face="宋体">个小时无法执行完成的状态。而只能分散插入。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">设计并不是讨论和思考，还需要去尝试，我认为当你的设计完成的时候，你的骨干核心代码都基本完成了。（多些时间能少写些代码）</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2.<font face="宋体">防止过度设计</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">我遇到的过度设计大多数源自于对需求理解不清楚，把非核心需求，或者很久之后的需求，当做高优先级的事情来满足。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">这种，需要把整个项目简化简化再简化。整个项目的可维护性也会大幅提升。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">3.<font face="宋体">不要过度压缩方案设计时间</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">之前我一直的节奏是，最多一个星期做方案设计，然后开始进入两到三星期的编码阶段。设计和研发的时间比例一般是</font>1<font face="宋体">：</font><font face="Calibri">3</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">现在想起来，这个时间分配是不合适的，技术方案设计阶段应该占整体时间的</font>50%<font face="宋体">。前期考虑的越周密，后期反复修改、调整方案的时间越少。整体来看是节省时间的。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">4.<font face="宋体">根据需求来反推设计</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">切忌先入为主，看哪个方案高大上或者容易实现，就开始用哪个技术方案。对于每一个技术方案，首先要想到该模块的应用场景，把每个应用场景分析清楚，在该应用场景下，应该选用哪个技术方案。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">4.<font face="宋体">排期</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">个人在排期上总是过于乐观。总是想着尽快把工作完成。其实有很多干扰因素。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">排期的时候，务必把事情考虑详细，具体执行步骤。同时还需要考虑到以下因素：</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">1.<font face="宋体">平时其他业务的干扰。平时我们不仅要做自己的项目，还有其他临时的业务需求，或者其他人来问问题等等，都有可能很耗时间。这部分时间导致，一个星期最多只有</font><font face="Calibri">3</font><font face="宋体">天的时间专注到长期规划的工作中。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2.<font face="宋体">延期的风险。每个项目，在原有计划的基础上，增加</font><font face="Calibri">20%</font><font face="宋体">的时间，来应对方案实施过程中各种异常情况。好比，某个细节没有考虑清楚等等。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">5.<font face="宋体">总结</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">聪明的程序员使用</font>50%-70%<font face="宋体">的时间用来思考，尝试和权衡各种设计和实现，而用</font><font face="Calibri">30% </font><font face="宋体">– </font><font face="Calibri">50%</font><font face="宋体">的时间是在忙碌着编码，调试和测试。聪明的老板也会让团队这样做。而傻逼的老板，苦逼的程序员会拿出来</font><font face="Calibri">100%-150%</font><font face="宋体">的时间来忙着赶进度，返工，重构，</font><font face="Calibri">fix </font><font face="宋体">大量的</font><font face="Calibri">bug</font><font face="宋体">… 所以， 越差的团队一般会越忙，而且还忙不完。（引自多些时间能少写些代码）</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:''yes'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                ', 89.5, 1422101);
